@startuml
title frontend - React 19 FSD (Feature-Sliced Design) 6 Layer 구조

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #F3E5F5
  BorderColor #8E24AA
}
skinparam component<<infra>> {
  BackgroundColor #E8F4FD
  BorderColor #2196F3
}
skinparam component<<external>> {
  BackgroundColor #ECEFF1
  BorderColor #607D8B
}

actor "사용자\n(Browser)" as User

package "app (전역)" {
  component "Router (React Router)\nProviders (Zustand · TanStack Query)\nGlobal Styles (Tailwind 4)" as App
}

package "pages (28개 페이지)" {
  component "landing · home\nlogin · sign-up\nforgot-password\nonboarding\nresume-{list,new,detail}\njd-{list,add,detail}\ninterview-{precheck,setup,session,results,complete,report}\nachievements · subscription\nsettings · notifications" as Pages
}

package "widgets" {
  component "interview-session\n(녹화 + 질문 표시)\nlanding-navbar" as Widgets
}

package "features (14개 슬라이스)" {
  component "auth\nhome\nonboarding\nresume\njd\nuser-job-description\ninterview-precheck\ninterview-setup\ninterview-session\nachievements · streak\nmilestones · notifications\nsubscription · settings" as Features
}

package "entities" {
  component "session\n(InterviewSession\n인터뷰 model)" as Entities
}

package "shared (공통 자원)" {
  component "ui (Button · Modal · Input)\napi (axios client · interceptor)\nlib (Zustand store · utils)\nconfig (env · routes)" as Shared
}

package "외부 의존" {
  component "Backend API\n(REST / WebSocket / SSE)" as BE <<external>>
  component "S3 Presigned PUT" as S3 <<external>>
  component "voice-api\n(TTS Bearer)" as VA <<external>>
  component "MediaRecorder API\n@mediapipe/tasks-vision\nGSAP + Lenis" as Browser <<infra>>
}

User --> App
App --> Pages
Pages --> Widgets
Pages --> Features
Widgets --> Features
Features --> Entities
Features --> Shared
Entities --> Shared

Features ..> Shared : api 클라이언트
Features --> BE : REST · WS · SSE
Features --> S3 : 멀티파트 업로드
Features --> VA : TTS
Widgets --> Browser : MediaRecorder

note bottom of App
  FSD 의존 방향:
  app → pages → widgets → features → entities → shared
  (상위 layer 가 하위 layer 만 import.
   cross-import 금지 = 같은 layer 내 슬라이스 간 import 금지)
end note

footer frontend/ — Feature-Sliced Design 6 layer, Zustand · TanStack Query · Tailwind 4
@enduml
